==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Swiftlet
<hw>Swift"let</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of numerous species of small East Indian and Asiatic swifts
of the genus <gen>Collocalia</gen>. Some of the species are noted for
furnishing the edible bird's nest. See <xex>Illust.</xex> under
<er>Edible</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Swiftly</ent>⟦br⟧
